                    "     }\n                    }\n                    `application: {\n              "
                    "        `global_theme: {\n                            values: (keys "
                    "*global_themes*)\n                        }\n                    }\n              "
                    "}  \n                \n              })```<br><br>The above will display the "
                    "*env_config* as a hierarchical form, with some values being completely "
